he low ac from being a leather only class hurts when you are soloing. The shaman spells you get are extremely watered down also. The plus to the class is the pet. Your pet buffs are the best buffs in the game. On high end raids the beastlord and the pet are awsome damage dealers and unless you dot the mob while in a group the main tank will almost always keep aggro.<br>
